---
// src/components/Framework.astro
---
<section class="framework-section" id="framework">
  <div class="framework-container">
    <div class="section-header">
      <h2 class="section-title">The Four Friction Points of AI-Enabled CX</h2>
      <p class="section-lead">
        Deploying a customer-facing AI model is simple. Driving cross-functional workflow adoption and measurable customer retention is where organizations fracture. We evaluate and solve for all four vectors.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="framework-grid">
      <!-- Pillar 1: Implementation -->
      <article class="framework-card">
        <div class="card-num">01</div>
        <h3 class="card-title">Smarter Implementation</h3>
        <p class="card-text">
          We integrate customer-facing systems within highly complex legacy environments. We map AI utilities directly to your existing operational bottlenecks, ensuring technical architecture aligns with business reality.
        </p>
      </article>

      <!-- Pillar 2: Trust -->
      <article class="framework-card">
        <div class="card-num">02</div>
        <h3 class="card-title">Stakeholder Trust</h3>
        <p class="card-text">
          AI systems are abandoned when teams don't trust the output. We translate intricate stakeholder requirements into transparent safeguards, protecting brand reputation while empowering frontline agents.
        </p>
      </article>

      <!-- Pillar 3: Adoption -->
      <article class="framework-card">
        <div class="card-num">03</div>
        <h3 class="card-title">Workflow Adoption</h3>
        <p class="card-text">
          A system is only as valuable as its utilization rate. We specialize in the human side of technological transition, designing frictionless internal loops that turn reluctant staff into active system power-users.
        </p>
      </article>

      <!-- Pillar 4: Measurement -->
      <article class="framework-card">
        <div class="card-num">04</div>
        <h3 class="card-title">CRM Measurement</h3>
        <p class="card-text">
          We don't measure success by API uptime. We leverage Salesforce and CRM data to trace a direct line between system interaction and concrete customer outcomes, proving real-world financial return on investment.
        </p>
      </article>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  /* --- DESIGN TOKENS (Spectrum 2 + SEO Semantic Layout) --- */
  .framework-section {
    width: 100%;
    padding: 100px 24px;
    background-color: var(--spectrum-background-layer-2, #f5f5f5);
  }

  .framework-container {
    max-width: 1200px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 64px;
  }

  /* --- HEADER (Optimized for Answer Engine snippets) --- */
  .section-header {
    max-width: 800px;
  }

  .section-title {
    font-family: adobe-clean, sans-serif;
    font-size: 36px;
    font-weight: 800;
    color: var(--spectrum-heading-color, CanvasText);
    letter-spacing: -0.02em;
    margin-bottom: 16px;
  }

  .section-lead {
    font-family: adobe-clean, sans-serif;
    font-size: 18px;
    line-height: 1.6;
    color: var(--spectrum-body-color, #4b4b4b);
  }

  /* --- GRID ARCHITECTURE --- */
  .framework-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
    gap: 32px;
  }

  .framework-card {
    background-color: var(--spectrum-background-layer-1, #ffffff);
    padding: 40px;
    border-radius: 6px;
    border: 1px solid rgba(var(--spectrum-gray-600-rgb, 108, 108, 108), 10%);
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 16px;
    box-shadow: 0 2px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.02);
  }

  .card-num {
    font-family: adobe-clean, sans-serif;
    font-size: 14px;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--spectrum-global-color-accent, #0265dc);
    letter-spacing: 0.1em;
  }

  .card-title {
    font-family: adobe-clean, sans-serif;
    font-size: 22px;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--spectrum-heading-color, CanvasText);
    letter-spacing: -0.01em;
  }

  .card-text {
    font-family: adobe-clean, sans-serif;
    font-size: 16px;
    line-height: 1.6;
    color: var(--spectrum-body-color, #4b4b4b);
  }

  /* --- 📱 RESPONSIVE SINGLE-TREE MEDIA QUERIES --- */
  @media (max-width: 900px) {
    .framework-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr; /* Flattens to single column seamlessly on mobile touch viewports */
      gap: 24px;
    }
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .framework-section {
      padding: 64px 16px;
    }
    
    .section-title {
      font-size: 28px;
    }
    
    .framework-card {
      padding: 24px;
    }
  }
</style>
